parameters: This guy, as expected, is strong...!

(They're not chasing after me, it seems they've been trained
to stick to their guard duty. I thought if I showed a gap,
maybe I could dodge and go deeper, but they won't let me do
that, huh.)

(Well, that's fine. I'll just get ready and keep confronting
them until I can get through!!)

It seems the magic path has been severed; it won't activate
anymore.
